overview:
SydCam is a multifacited electronics service company. That is able to provide a wide range of services and products to best fit your needs. Computers, CCTV systems, IP camera systems, VOIP systems, Phone systems, Intercom Access systems. With over 17 years in the business!

At SydCam we pride ourselves on our ability to service a wide range of electronics issues. It doesn’t matter if its basic network setup, designing & building a network, installation of a router, or running wire for telephone service….we can do it all!

SydCam also provides both commercial and residential Security & Fire Alarm Monitoring and Installation service.
